	<h1 class="title">Lanvin也出事了，时尚界的设计总监越来越像流水的兵</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Vanessa Friedman</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-29 17:02:50 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16787/medium/16787.jpg?1446104077" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


